<p>Stewart Brand writes in his newest section:</p><blockquote><p>A FUNDAMENTAL QUESTION that will keep coming up is this: What are the best ways to <em>design</em> for maintenance?  At the very beginning of the auto industry, no less than three radically different design-for-maintenance philosophies fought it out.  One lost, but not because of maintenance issues.  The other two won big by rejecting each other’s approach to maintenance.</p></blockquote><p>Read the piece <a href="https://books.worksinprogress.co/book/maintenance-of-everything/vehicles/three-maintenance-philosophies-fought-for-control-of-the-auto-industry/1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">here</a>. Collaborate <a href="https://books.worksinprogress.co/book/maintenance-of-everything/vehicles/three-maintenance-philosophies-fought-for-control-of-the-auto-industry/1?mode=suggest" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">here</a>. </p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6bdb7372-8b0b-4fec-a520-bef9a5d0104f_1024x779.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/cJWCi27Pb3TlbZMuHFnoZXo477y- 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux. 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/gtXWsZYRE8N3bc-zWp283SyA7cIDaGPjOT3zm5Eu-p4=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGNmJkYjczNzItOGIwYi00ZmVjLWE1MjAtYmVmOWE1ZDAxMDRmXzEwMjR4Nzc5LmpwZWc= 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/GdYrUAn8QMxaAqcyC-" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/3fuD69eJoKB4xPjrER0xeEgTc0aiol-